Go tool to modify/update field tags in structs. gomodifytags makes it easy to
update, add or delete the tags in a struct field. You can easily add new
tags, update existing tags (such as appending a new key, i.e: db, xml, etc..)
or remove existing tags. It also allows you to add and remove tag options.
It's intended to be used by an editor, but also has modes to run it from the
terminal. Read the usage section below for more information.
